  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oil in a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion and garlic; sauté until softened.",
    "Stir in tomato paste, cook for an additional minute.",
    "Pour in dry sherry, reduce to half of its volume (about 1 tablespoon).",
    "Gradually add chicken broth, stirring frequently. Let it simmer for about 5 minutes or until the liquid has reduced slightly.",
    "Add heavy cream and butter; stir well.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with fresh dill if desired."
